Casablanca,t2jBSAWCg5s,Ugwt-HqYbDvAKi2lhyd4AaABAg,,@seantlewis376,"This is the most beautiful, most lovely love story of all time.
In 2018, my British girlfriend of 10 years broke up with me. It took place at the Portland Airport as I was walking her through. I turned around to walk away. After a few steps, I paused. I looked behind me to see her going through the security gates. I touched my fingers to my lips from fifty feet away. She turned, looked at me, and put her fingers to her lips. We have not seen each other since.
