Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgyO3AOnHKt8PK53Rnl4AaABAg.AS_QqDuYUnpASyAQWSCbPZ,UgyO3AOnHKt8PK53Rnl4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Have you spent any time at all in the US during the current administration? And while we're sorry to hear what you're dealing with, there is corruption everywhere. Your issue is something that many countries also face, not just Morocco. So while you might think it's worse than in other places, it's not so different at all. 

But we found the people friendly and kind and we had lovely experiences there, especially in Fes. We think it's worth visiting Morocco to meet its people and understand its culture. A country is more than its government. —Judy",2026-02-08T11:10:53Z,2026-02-08T11:10:53Z,0,True,,2026-05-12T02:02:08.716293
