Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugz2Hkon2jQQPz-Y6nN4AaABAg.ARh4x-gVtsNARh5UIugA81,Ugz2Hkon2jQQPz-Y6nN4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Hi Zach, They really are close to each other, and a lot of people enjoy doing them together. We ended up skipping the YSL Museum this time because most of the exhibits don’t allow photography. Since we rely on photos and video for our channel, it wasn’t the best fit for us, especially due to the cost. We have a budget and we knew we would be hitting the limit when we visited the Sahara Desert. But it’s definitely a beautiful stop for anyone visiting Marrakech! Thanks for watching. —Judy
