Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugzw0hdsOOdS-EeaQdx4AaABAg.AD7aowz4S8bAD7dDFFgaiS,Ugzw0hdsOOdS-EeaQdx4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Hi Ike, We really enjoyed Morocco as well. You should visit Fes on your next trip. We missed Essaouira, but we did do a Sahara Desert tour, which we highly recommend. I'll link our other videos below. We were very fortunate to be able to be in Morocco for over 40 days! —Judy
