Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugx_uGmjXey5dDUuYeN4AaABAg.ABKSonVD4xDABLapaHulVy,Ugx_uGmjXey5dDUuYeN4AaABAg,@TranLe-vy5nz,@ Thank you so much for your tips . I love all your videos❤️❤️❤️,2024-11-27T13:27:04Z,2024-11-27T13:27:04Z,0,True,,2026-05-12T02:02:16.539658
Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugx_uGmjXey5dDUuYeN4AaABAg.ABKSonVD4xDABLbJdAbzw5,Ugx_uGmjXey5dDUuYeN4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,@TranLe-vy5nz Thank you! We are grateful to hear this. We appreciate your support more than you know! -Judy,2024-11-27T13:31:18Z,2024-11-27T13:31:18Z,1,True,,2026-05-12T02:02:16.539663
