Tanger,HQnJ1mOgw9E,UgzgEaFp-Hx0otQ2Wgh4AaABAg,,@TheGlitch096,"I found this song randomly on Spotify and found that this music video exists. I'm someone that suffers from really bad memory loss to the point that I *do* forget people, and this hits hard. Absolutely beautiful song, and the animation fits so much of it so well. Even though it hits too close to home, I love it.",2025-11-12T18:42:14Z,2025-11-12T18:42:14Z,11,False,0.0,2026-05-12T02:04:00.764255
